    <entry>
      <title>Markdown Notes</title>
      <link href="/2018/12/20/md-notes/"/>
      <url>/2018/12/20/md-notes/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown-Basics"><a href="#Markdown-Basics" class="headerlink" title="Markdown Basics"></a>Markdown Basics</h1><h2 id="Good-Referrences"><a href="#Good-Referrences" class="headerlink" title="Good Referrences"></a>Good Referrences</h2><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/q81RER" target="_blank" rel="noopener">简书官方教程</a></p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUBNt18RFbo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A YouTube Tutorial</a></p><h2 id="Recommended-Environment"><a href="#Recommended-Environment" class="headerlink" title="Recommended Environment"></a>Recommended Environment</h2><p>Vscode + markdownlint + Auto-Open Markdown Preview</p><h2 id="Syntax-Essentials"><a href="#Syntax-Essentials" class="headerlink" title="Syntax Essentials"></a>Syntax Essentials</h2><ol><li><p>Headings</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># Heading1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## Heading 2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### Heading 3</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><h1 id="Heading1"><a href="#Heading1" class="headerlink" title="Heading1"></a>Heading1</h1><h2 id="Heading2"><a href="#Heading2" class="headerlink" title="Heading2"></a>Heading2</h2><h3 id="Heading3"><a href="#Heading3" class="headerlink" title="Heading3"></a>Heading3</h3></li><li><p>Italics</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*this text*</span> is italic</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_this text_</span> is italic</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><p><em>this text</em> is italic</p><p><em>this text</em> is italic</p></li><li><p>Strong</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**this text**</span> is strong</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__this text__</span> is strong</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><p><strong>this text</strong> is strong</p><p><strong>this text</strong> is strong</p></li><li><p>Strikethrough</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~this text~~ is striked through</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><p><del>this text</del> is striked through</p></li><li><p>Horizontal Rule</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">___</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><hr><hr></li><li><p>Blockquote</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;this text is a blockquote</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><blockquote><p>this text is a blockquote</p></blockquote></li><li><p>Links</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">linkname</span>](<span class="link">link-url</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- with title--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">linkname</span>](<span class="link">link-url "titlename"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><p><a href="https://williamlwclwc.github.io">william’s-blog</a></p><p><a href="https://williamlwclwc.github.io" title="my-blog">william’s-blog</a></p></li><li><p>Unordered List</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>Item 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>Item 2</span><br><span class="line">  * Nested Item 1</span><br><span class="line">  * Nested Item 2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><ul><li>Item 1</li><li>Item 2<ul><li>Nested Item 1</li><li>Nested Item 2</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>Ordered List</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>Item 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>Item 2</span><br><span class="line">  1. Nested Item 1</span><br><span class="line">  2. Nested Item 2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><ol><li>Item 1</li><li>Item 2</li><li>Nested Item 1</li><li>Nested Item 2</li></ol></li><li><p>Code Blocks</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`&lt;p&gt;This is an inline code block&lt;/p&gt;`</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- get rid of '\' while implementing--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">\<span class="code">`\`</span>\`language-name</span><br><span class="line">import numpy as np</span><br><span class="line">\<span class="code">`\`</span>\`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><p><code>&lt;p&gt;This is an inline code block&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Images</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">Markdown Logo</span>](<span class="link">https://markdown-here.com/img/icon256.png</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><p><img src="https://markdown-here.com/img/icon256.png" alt="Markdown Logo"></p></li><li><p>Task List</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>[x] Task1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>[x] Task2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>[ ] Task3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p><ul><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox" checked> Task1</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox" checked> Task2</li><li style="list-style: none"><input type="checkbox"> Task3</li></ul></li><li><p>Tables</p><p>code:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| Tables        | Syntax        | Are           |</span><br><span class="line">| ------------- |:-------------:| -------------:|</span><br><span class="line">| col 3 is      | "----------:" | right-aligned |</span><br><span class="line">| col 2 is      | ":---------:" | centered      |</span><br><span class="line">| col 1 is      | "-----------" | left-aligned  |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>effects:</p></li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>Tables</th><th>Syntax</th><th>Are</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>col 3 is</td><td>“———-:”</td><td>right-aligned</td></tr><tr><td>col 2 is</td><td>“:———:”</td><td>centered</td></tr><tr><td>col 1 is</td><td>“———–”</td><td>left-aligned</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Programming languages </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
