        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Introduction"><a href="#Introduction" class="headerlink" title="Introduction"></a>Introduction</h1><p>Welcome to my coding blog, this is my first post, thanks to the tutorial on how to build a blog with Hexo and this open-source theme melody.</p><p>The following tutorial links are Chinese.</p><h2 id="Create-a-blog-using-hexo"><a href="#Create-a-blog-using-hexo" class="headerlink" title="Create a blog using hexo"></a>Create a blog using hexo</h2><p>Tutorial Link: <a href="https://my.oschina.net/ryaneLee/blog/638440" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tutorial on how to build your own blog with Hexo</a></p><h2 id="Hexo-Theme-melody"><a href="#Hexo-Theme-melody" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Theme: melody"></a>Hexo Theme: melody</h2><p>More info: <a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/hexo-theme-melody" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Theme: melody</a></p><h2 id="How-to-let-your-blog-got-searched-on-Baidu-amp-Google"><a href="#How-to-let-your-blog-got-searched-on-Baidu-amp-Google" class="headerlink" title="How to let your blog got searched on Baidu &amp; Google"></a>How to let your blog got searched on Baidu &amp; Google</h2><p>Tutorial Link: <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/25145964abf3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tutorial on how to add your blog in Google &amp; Baidu</a></p><p>Another tutorial: <a href="http://tengj.github.io/2016/03/14/hexo6seo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tutorial on how to add your blog in Google &amp; Baidu</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
